high_descs: Walk forward and turn right to face the stove.
Pick up the square pan on the front right burner of the stove.
Turn to the right, walk forward to face the sink.
Place the square pan into the sink, turn on the water, fill the pan with water, turn the water off and pick the pan up out of the sink.
Turn around, cross the room and face the stove to your right.
Place the square pan back on the stove on the front right burner.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the square pan fill it with water and return the pan to the stove.

high_descs: Walk forward to the wall then turn right and walk to the stove
Pick up the pan that is on the lower right burner of the stove
Turn right and cross the room to the sink
Place the pan into the sink and turn on the faucet. Fill up the pan then turn off the faucet and pick the pan up
Turn around and cross the room to the stove, turn and face the stove
Place the pan on the bottom right burner of the stove
anns.task_desc: Place a pan containing water on a stove

high_descs: move forward and locate the gas
pick up the pan from the gas
turn right and move towards the sink
fill up the pan with water
turn around and move towards the gas
place the pan back on the gas
anns.task_desc: place a pan filled with water on the gas
